lyrics:
[verse]
I went walking, in the Russian night
Searching for a taste, that felt just right
Шашлык sizzling, on the grill so bright
Every bite, a culinary delight

[chorus]
Шашлык красивое, oh so divine
Grilled perfection, under stars that shine
Шашлык красивое, take me away
In this delicious moment, I want to stay
